Three global flags are accepted on EVERY subcommand (including help, skill, version): --json, --no-color, --color={auto,always,never}. These are stripped from args by a global pre-pass BEFORE per-subcommand flag validation runs. They never appear in any command's Meta().Flags list. They never trigger unknown_flag_rejection. See <ref spec="cli.unknown_flag_rejection">unknown flag rejection</ref> for the updated rule.